Timeline of Westminster terrorist attack: How events unfolded (STREET VIEW) Timeline of Westminster terrorist attack: How events unfolded (STREET VIEW) By 0 11 
As the people of London cope with the aftermath of Wednesday’s terrorist attack at Westminster, RT takes a look back at the day that shook both the city and the world in what was London’s deadliest attack since 2005.
